term: hamburger menu
---
definition:

It's a icon with three horizontal lines usually on the top-left corner or top-right corner of the screen.
By clicking or tapping on the icon, it reveals a menu with options or additional pages.

Reference: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hamburger_button

